Feature: Make webapplication available off-line
    In order to continue working when there is no internet connection
    as a user
    I want to have off-line access to the webapplication and to records i am likely to need
    
    A local cache of records is taken care of by the local cache feature. This means the application itself and any other assests such as images, stylesheets and so one should be available in the browser without a connection.
    
    Scenario: I am using the application and my connection is broken.
    
    Scenario: I am using the application offline and my connection comes back on.
    
    Scenario: a new version of the webappliation is available.
    
    Scenario: no new version of the webapplication is available.
    
    Scenario: resources fail to load.
    

  
